    "pubDate": "2026-03-23T14:36:22.000Z",
    "content": "<p><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=%27http://www.w3.org/2000/svg%27%20width='1000'%20height='450'%20viewBox=%270%200%201000%20450%27%3E%3C/svg%3E\" loading=\"lazy\" data-lazy=\"1\" width=\"1000\" height=\"450\" data-tf-src=\"https://media20.org/wp-content/uploads/2026/06/M20-policy-document-_-Jep-Gambardella-Pexels-3.png\" class=\"tf_svg_lazy attachment-full size-full wp-post-image\" alt=\"\" data-tf-srcset=\"https://media20.org/wp-content/uploads/2026/06/M20-policy-document-_-Jep-Gambardella-Pexels-3.png 1000w, https://media20.org/wp-content/uploads/2026/06/M20-policy-document-_-Jep-Gambardella-Pexels-3-300x135.png 300w, https://media20.org/wp-content/uploads/2026/06/M20-policy-document-_-Jep-Gambardella-Pexels-3-768x346.png 768w, https://media20.org/wp-content/uploads/2026/06/M20-policy-document-_-Jep-Gambardella-Pexels-3-500x225.png 500w, https://media20.org/wp-content/uploads/2026/06/M20-policy-document-_-Jep-Gambardella-Pexels-3-1280x576.png 1280w\" data-tf-sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\"><noscript><img width=\"1000\" height=\"450\" data-tf-not-load src=\"https://media20.org/wp-content/uploads/2026/06/M20-policy-document-_-Jep-Gambardella-Pexels-3.png\" class=\"attachment-full size-full wp-post-image\" alt=\"\" decoding=\"async\" srcset=\"https://media20.org/wp-content/uploads/2026/06/M20-policy-document-_-Jep-Gambardella-Pexels-3.png 1000w, https://media20.org/wp-content/uploads/2026/06/M20-policy-document-_-Jep-Gambardella-Pexels-3-300x135.png 300w, https://media20.org/wp-content/uploads/2026/06/M20-policy-document-_-Jep-Gambardella-Pexels-3-768x346.png 768w, https://media20.org/wp-content/uploads/2026/06/M20-policy-document-_-Jep-Gambardella-Pexels-3-500x225.png 500w, https://media20.org/wp-content/uploads/2026/06/M20-policy-document-_-Jep-Gambardella-Pexels-3-1280x576.png 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\" /></noscript></p>\n<p>The <a href=\"https://media20.org/2025/09/02/m20-johannesburg-declaration/\">M20 Johannesburg Declaration</a> was a result of a collaborative global discussion in 2025 that set a foundation for information-sharing to ensure that the G20 integrates information integrity, press freedom and media sustainability into a broader development financing architecture.</p>",
