  {
    "title": "SANEF congratulates The African Editors Forum for the successful hosting of the African Editors Congress 2026",
    "link": "https://media20.org/2026/03/04/sanef-congratulates-the-african-editors-forum-taef-for-the-successful-hosting-of-the-african-editors-congress-2026-and-its-agm/",
    "pubDate": "2026-03-04T08:04:54.000Z",
    "content": "<p><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=%27http://www.w3.org/2000/svg%27%20width='1000'%20height='450'%20viewBox=%270%200%201000%20450%27%3E%3C/svg%3E\" loading=\"lazy\" data-lazy=\"1\" width=\"1000\" height=\"450\" data-tf-src=\"https://media20.org/wp-content/uploads/2026/06/M20-press-release-_-Kim-Nowacki-Flickr-CC-BY-ND.png\" class=\"tf_svg_lazy attachment-full size-full wp-post-image\" alt=\"Kim Nowacki, Flickr - CC BY-ND\" data-tf-srcset=\"https://media20.org/wp-content/uploads/2026/06/M20-press-release-_-Kim-Nowacki-Flickr-CC-BY-ND.png 1000w, https://media20.org/wp-content/uploads/2026/06/M20-press-release-_-Kim-Nowacki-Flickr-CC-BY-ND-300x135.png 300w, https://media20.org/wp-content/uploads/2026/06/M20-press-release-_-Kim-Nowacki-Flickr-CC-BY-ND-768x346.png 768w, https://media20.org/wp-content/uploads/2026/06/M20-press-release-_-Kim-Nowacki-Flickr-CC-BY-ND-1280x576.png 1280w, https://media20.org/wp-content/uploads/2026/06/M20-press-release-_-Kim-Nowacki-Flickr-CC-BY-ND-500x225.png 500w\" data-tf-sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\"><noscript><img width=\"1000\" height=\"450\" data-tf-not-load src=\"https://media20.org/wp-content/uploads/2026/06/M20-press-release-_-Kim-Nowacki-Flickr-CC-BY-ND.png\" class=\"attachment-full size-full wp-post-image\" alt=\"Kim Nowacki, Flickr - CC BY-ND\" decoding=\"async\" srcset=\"https://media20.org/wp-content/uploads/2026/06/M20-press-release-_-Kim-Nowacki-Flickr-CC-BY-ND.png 1000w, https://media20.org/wp-content/uploads/2026/06/M20-press-release-_-Kim-Nowacki-Flickr-CC-BY-ND-300x135.png 300w, https://media20.org/wp-content/uploads/2026/06/M20-press-release-_-Kim-Nowacki-Flickr-CC-BY-ND-768x346.png 768w, https://media20.org/wp-content/uploads/2026/06/M20-press-release-_-Kim-Nowacki-Flickr-CC-BY-ND-1280x576.png 1280w, https://media20.org/wp-content/uploads/2026/06/M20-press-release-_-Kim-Nowacki-Flickr-CC-BY-ND-500x225.png 500w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\" /></noscript></p>\n<p>L